The Swimming Club is currently recruiting members!! If

"Guaranteed D for next year's graduates!! The leading

\FF[momoha_smile]Momoha: "Gotcha! Stop right there. I'm going to arrest
you~♪"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[momoha_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "A police officer strutting around inside the school
like she owns the place...! It's not that dangerous here!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[momoha_smile]\AA[2]Momoha: "Oh? But there's a monster walking around attacking
people~? Must be a pretty dangerous place, huh?"

\FF[momoha_reverse]Momoha: "Bingo~♪ Kyahaha!! Ah, it was me, I'm that monster!!
I just love attacking cute, cute high school girls like
you~♪"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[momoha_reverse]\AA[1]Akane: "The one who's supposed to protect is the
attacker...! It's quite distressing and subtly annoying!"

\F[beni_reverse1]\FF[momoha_reverse]\AA[1]Akane: "But you know~, if you're not discerning, you might
let your prey escape~♪ Maybe I'm already a monster just like
you, Onee-san♪"

\F[beni_reverse1]\FF[momoha_reverse]\AA[2]Momoha: "!? Seriously~! What a waste calling out to you~! My
hobby is to torment scared kids, after all~!"

\F[beni_reverse1]\FF[momoha_reverse]\AA[2]Momoha: "You should try it too! It's super addictive, you
know~!!"

\FF[momoha_reverse]Momoha: "Ahh♥ I just love attacking cute, cute high school
girls~♪"
